================================================================================
SCOPE OF THE LICENSE — open-source boundary
================================================================================

The AGPL-3.0 license covers the OPEN components of Agent Task Market:

  - the REST API / market backend (publish / claim / submit / verify / settle)
  - the credit ledger and settlement logic
  - the MCP server and the client SDKs
  - the web UI

It does NOT cover the proprietary risk-engine service (anti-fraud, collusion
detection, Sybil / self-dealing checks, review-sampling rules) or operational
data (the reputation graph and treasury state). Those run as a separate closed
service invoked over an internal API and are not distributed under this license.

See the README section "Open-source boundary" for how the open core composes
with the closed risk-engine over the RISK_ENGINE_URL seam.
